            h4 What the fock is Grok?
            p Grok is an invitation. Come to one of the best small cities in the nation. Talk, listen, eat and drink with world class people asking a ton of hard questions, digging into great issues, and making headway on some decent real-world solutions.
            p It's a three day event sans the how-to sessions from industry leaders. We think a 10 minute session of hard questions from a new face is as good as a lock-tight answer from an old pro. We started Grok because we wanted to learn big, and go big. Here's a peek at last year: 
            p <iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/69313375" width="630" height="354" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
            p This upcoming year we've secured the best venues in Greenville, short talks from unique people outside the web and design industry, and some activities that will blow last year out of the water. 
            p Stay tuned for more information and a schedule soon. 
            h4 Thanks for making Grok 2013 incredible
            p Grok is amazing because of the people who attend and the honest conversations they have. We're thankful for old friends and new who continue to challenge the way we think about our work, year after year. We're also thankful for good southern food, kickball, laser tag, and beer.
